sequenceDiagram
    participant Dev as Developer
    participant GH as GitHub
    participant Runner as ubuntu-latest Runner
    participant Black
    participant Ruff
    participant Mypy
    participant Pytest
    participant Render as Render (Produktion)

    Dev->>GH: git push (main)
    GH->>Runner: Trigger CI/CD workflow

    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Note over Runner: CI – Qualitaetssicherung
        Runner->>Runner: Checkout code
        Runner->>Runner: Setup Python 3.12
        Runner->>Runner: pip install -r requirements-dev.txt
        Runner->>Black: black --check .
        Black-->>Runner: Format OK / Fail
        Runner->>Ruff: ruff check .
        Ruff-->>Runner: Lint OK / Fail
        Runner->>Mypy: mypy app/
        Mypy-->>Runner: Types OK / Fail
        Runner->>Pytest: pytest tests/ -v
        Pytest-->>Runner: Tests OK / Fail
    end

    alt Alle Checks bestanden
        rect rgb(240, 255, 240)
            Note over Runner: CD – Deployment
            Runner->>Render: Deploy Hook (HTTPS POST)
            Render-->>Runner: 200 OK – Build gestartet
            Render->>Render: Build + Release
        end

        rect rgb(255, 248, 240)
            Note over Runner: Monitoring
            Runner->>Runner: Wait 30s (Deployment-Zeit)
            Runner->>Render: GET /health
            Render-->>Runner: 200 {"status": "ok"}
            Runner-->>GH: Pipeline erfolgreich
        end
    else Check fehlgeschlagen
        Runner-->>GH: Pipeline fehlgeschlagen
        GH-->>Dev: Fehler-Benachrichtigung
    end

    GH-->>Dev: Status (pass/fail)
